    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 8 Creation Points </p><p>Keyword: Weapon </p><p>Drain: 10 CCD Chakra </p><p></p><p>You equip your Titan with explosive tools in the event of a disaster.</p><p> When your Titan reaches 0 hit points and you would eject from it, you can spend the CCD Drain to cause the Titan to explode.</p><p> When you do this, you are ejected 90 feet away from the mech instead.</p><p> All creatures within a 30-foot radius of the Titan must make a Dexterity saving throw, taking Xd10 fire damage (where X is your proficiency bonus) on a failed save, or half as much on a success.</p><p></p>",
